frames.caption: A mystical scene unfolds in an enchanted forest, where a luminous woman in a flowing gown walks barefoot along a flower-lined path. She is surrounded by three imposing figures with mythical features, including horns and pointed ears, who stand solemnly among the trees. The atmosphere is ethereal, with soft light filtering through the foliage, casting a magical glow on the scene.
